  "text": "Phenols were extracted from 0.3 g of fresh-weight (FW) tissue (fruit pericarp) in 80% methanol, assayed using the Folin-Ciocalteu reagent following standard methods and expressed as mg gallic acid equivalents (GAE g -1 FW), used for the standard curve with a range of 0-125 µM [CITATION_1] .",
